LOVE ROBOT FROM SPACE

Programming / Graphics:
	Sven <Svenstaro> Haase
	Paul <Opatut> Bienkowski
	Matz <Timesqueezer> Radloff

Controls:
    == Global Keys ==
    Tab:    Toggle editor mode
    Escape: Quit

    == Game Mode ==
    Right:      Run right
    Left:       Run left
    1st Space:  Jump
    2nd Space:  Double jump
    Up:         Jetpack
    
    == Editor Mode ==
    Arrows:     Scroll view
    C:          Create entity
    X:          Delete current entity
    S:          Scale current entity
    R:          Rotate current entity
    G:          Grab current entity
    E:          Next image
    W:          Previous image
    N:          Name entity
    A:          Change entity alpha
    P:          Pause entity physics
    1-9:        Change layer
    F:          Move entity 1 layer up
    V:          Move entity 1 layer down
    F1:         Save world
    F2:         Reload world (Warning: changes are lost!)
    Return:     Accept
    Click:      Accept
    Rightclick: Select Entity

Special thanks to:
    hamsteralliance.com - Music track: Where am I?
